apotheosis means

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:36.150 align:middle line:84%
to raise from the human
realm of the divine,

00:02:36.150 --> 00:02:38.800 align:middle line:90%
and it means to ascend.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:43.010 align:middle line:10%
