has gone through it?

00:02:51.850 --> 00:02:52.850 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, I said.

00:02:52.850 --> 00:02:55.635 align:middle line:84%
This is exactly what
this symbolism shows.

00:02:55.635 --> 00:03:00.210 align:middle line:84%
The US Capitol dome is
every bit as profound

00:03:00.210 --> 00:03:02.280 align:middle line:84%
