in the US Capitol

00:04:00.710 --> 00:04:03.750 align:middle line:84%
as I describe them in my video,
The American Right, which

00:04:03.750 --> 00:04:07.260 align:middle line:84%
included my early research
on the Capitol dome.

00:04:07.260 --> 00:04:09.500 align:middle line:84%
