that the dome is actually

00:04:18.709 --> 00:04:22.780 align:middle line:84%
a model of our pineal
gland, the soul's gateway.

00:04:22.780 --> 00:04:24.780 align:middle line:84%
Dan Brown actually
had Robert Langdon

00:04:24.780 --> 00:04:27.830 align:middle line:84%
do the same thing in "The
Lost Symbol," even describing

00:04:27.830 --> 00:04:29.330 align:middle line:84%
the dome is like
the pineal gland

00:04:29.330 --> 00:04:31.882 align:middle line:84%
and seeing it open
like a star gate.

00:04:31.882 --> 00:04:33.590 align:middle line:84%
