00:04:43.310 --> 00:04:47.230 align:middle line:84%
To me, Constantino
Brumidi was crystal clear

00:04:47.230 --> 00:04:49.490 align:middle line:84%
that he believed
George Washington had

00:04:49.490 --> 00:04:52.550 align:middle line:90%
