showed this comparison,

00:04:55.220 --> 00:04:57.840 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Gray and I saw
utter astonishment

00:04:57.840 --> 00:05:00.320 align:middle line:84%
on the faces of the
experts at the Architect

00:05:00.320 --> 00:05:02.210 align:middle line:90%
