Christ on a rainbow,

00:05:19.850 --> 00:05:24.690 align:middle line:84%
but also the Tibetan depictions
of the rainbow body of light.

00:05:24.690 --> 00:05:27.320 align:middle line:84%
This is an extraordinary
observation

00:05:27.320 --> 00:05:30.460 align:middle line:84%
that had never been made
before, and opened up

00:05:30.460 --> 00:05:34.130 align:middle line:84%
