00:06:00.490 --> 00:06:04.180 align:middle line:84%
To me, the most astonishing
code symbol in the Capitol

00:06:04.180 --> 00:06:06.060 align:middle line:84%
is not just that
George Washington

00:06:06.060 --> 00:06:08.790 align:middle line:84%
is shown on a rainbow
in the celestial realms

00:06:08.790 --> 00:06:10.770 align:middle line:84%
as an ascended
being, but that he

00:06:10.770 --> 00:06:15.660 align:middle line:84%
is surrounded by 13 maidens
with stars on their heads.

00:06:15.660 --> 00:06:18.070 align:middle line:90%
These are celestial beings.

00:06:18.070 --> 00:06:19.800 align:middle line:84%
Now when you're in
the Capitol, guides

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:23.010 align:middle line:84%
will tell you that these
13 maidens represent the 13

00:06:23.010 --> 00:06:24.490 align:middle line:90%
