00:06:24.490 --> 00:06:25.960 align:middle line:90%
But I say, hold on.

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:28.560 align:middle line:90%
This is a heavenly scene.

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:30.040 align:middle line:90%
What's going on here?

00:06:30.040 --> 00:06:31.860 align:middle line:84%
Well, my answer is
that the Tibetans

00:06:31.860 --> 00:06:35.840 align:middle line:84%
teach that the rainbow body
practice is taught in 13 star

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:37.940 align:middle line:90%
systems, including our own.

00:06:37.940 --> 00:06:39.720 align:middle line:84%
I began to wonder,
is it possible

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:43.420 align:middle line:84%
that the 13 celestial maidens
around George Washington

00:06:43.420 --> 00:06:47.290 align:middle line:84%
represent the 13 star
systems, or star colonies,

00:06:47.290 --> 00:06:51.210 align:middle line:84%
of which our earth
and soul are part of?

00:06:51.210 --> 00:06:54.020 align:middle line:84%
If so, think of
the ramifications

00:06:54.020 --> 00:06:55.890 align:middle line:90%
of this disclosure.

00:06:55.890 --> 00:06:59.900 align:middle line:84%
Do souls really come and go
between these star systems

00:06:59.900 --> 00:07:03.910 align:middle line:84%
via a system of star gates
and wormholes as I proposed?

00:07:03.910 --> 00:07:06.980 align:middle line:84%
Does the US
government know this?

00:07:06.980 --> 00:07:11.350 align:middle line:84%
Was the founder of the nation
shown the secrets of ascension?

00:07:11.350 --> 00:07:14.500 align:middle line:84%
Is this why he's portrayed
as a resurrected human

00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:16.430 align:middle line:90%
in the Capitol?

00:07:16.430 --> 00:07:19.690 align:middle line:84%
Historically,
Washington was revered

00:07:19.690 --> 00:07:23.310 align:middle line:84%
as an ordinary man who
was able to accomplish

00:07:23.310 --> 00:07:26.930 align:middle line:84%
the extraordinary, even
spiritual extraordinary when he

00:07:26.930 --> 00:07:29.890 align:middle line:84%
led the first Americans to
freedom and the founding

00:07:29.890 --> 00:07:32.230 align:middle line:84%
of a new nation
dedicated to freedom

00:07:32.230 --> 00:07:35.090 align:middle line:84%
and the liberty
of the individual.

00:07:35.090 --> 00:07:38.490 align:middle line:84%
What many Americans and people
around the world don't realize

00:07:38.490 --> 00:07:44.520 align:middle line:84%
is that the Freemasons eulogized
George Washington as Enoch, one

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:47.850 align:middle line:90%
of the first humans to ascend.

00:07:47.850 --> 00:07:50.550 align:middle line:84%
In the story, Enoch
was taken to heaven

00:07:50.550 --> 00:07:52.950 align:middle line:84%
by the Archangel
Michael, who anointed him

00:07:52.950 --> 00:07:56.740 align:middle line:84%
with an oil that dissolved
his body into rainbow light.

00:07:56.740 --> 00:07:59.940 align:middle line:84%
Once Enoch attained
this light being status,

00:07:59.940 --> 00:08:03.260 align:middle line:84%
he gained the ability to
fluidly morph or phase

00:08:03.260 --> 00:08:07.280 align:middle line:84%
between his light body
state and flesh and blood.

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:09.090 align:middle line:90%
Think about that.

00:08:09.090 --> 00:08:11.490 align:middle line:84%
Are the Freemasons
actually implying

00:08:11.490 --> 00:08:17.090 align:middle line:84%
that George Washington was the
reincarnated soul of Enoch?

00:08:17.090 --> 00:08:18.820 align:middle line:90%
Let's look at some evidence.

00:08:18.820 --> 00:08:21.500 align:middle line:84%
Depictions I found in
museums in Philadelphia

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:25.480 align:middle line:84%
and New York of Washington
after his death stunningly

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:28.820 align:middle line:84%
portrayed him ascending
into heaven just

00:08:28.820 --> 00:08:31.110 align:middle line:90%
like the story of Enoch.

00:08:31.110 --> 00:08:34.309 align:middle line:84%
This engraving by J.J.
Barralet from 1800

00:08:34.309 --> 00:08:38.259 align:middle line:84%
is based on a sermon delivered
after Washington's death

00:08:38.259 --> 00:08:41.830 align:middle line:90%
equating Washington to Enoch.

00:08:41.830 --> 00:08:45.550 align:middle line:84%
Again, did the Freemasons
and ordinary Americans

00:08:45.550 --> 00:08:48.530 align:middle line:84%
of the early 1800s
actually believe

00:08:48.530 --> 00:08:52.090 align:middle line:84%
that George Washington was
a reincarnation of Enoch

00:08:52.090 --> 00:08:54.580 align:middle line:90%
and that he too ascended?

00:08:54.580 --> 00:09:00.140 align:middle line:84%
Think about this possibility
and what it actually means.

00:09:00.140 --> 00:09:03.050 align:middle line:84%
In this 1800 Apotheosis
of Washington,

00:09:03.050 --> 00:09:06.390 align:middle line:84%
we see an angel placing
the wreath of immortality

00:09:06.390 --> 00:09:08.560 align:middle line:90%
on Washington's head.

00:09:08.560 --> 00:09:12.970 align:middle line:84%
In this example, Washington is
raised like Jesus from the tomb

00:09:12.970 --> 00:09:17.290 align:middle line:84%
upon a shaft of light by the
spiritual and temporal genius

00:09:17.290 --> 00:09:20.430 align:middle line:90%
assisted by immortality.

00:09:20.430 --> 00:09:27.110 align:middle line:84%
And he ascends through a
sun gate or a star gate.

00:09:27.110 --> 00:09:31.040 align:middle line:84%
In this final example, we
see Washington as a Freemason

00:09:31.040 --> 00:09:33.110 align:middle line:84%
standing on a
checkerboard, the symbol

00:09:33.110 --> 00:09:35.880 align:middle line:90%
of the matrix of earth life.

00:09:35.880 --> 00:09:39.860 align:middle line:84%
A ladder extends from
his right shoulder.

00:09:39.860 --> 00:09:43.510 align:middle line:84%
The latter extends into
a rainbow hole in heaven,

00:09:43.510 --> 00:09:47.410 align:middle line:84%
or a rip in the
fabric of space time.

00:09:47.410 --> 00:09:50.240 align:middle line:84%
To me, this shows
Washington's dissolution

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:53.940 align:middle line:84%
into pure energy and his
attainment of the rainbow light

00:09:53.940 --> 00:09:55.140 align:middle line:90%
body.

00:09:55.140 --> 00:09:57.230 align:middle line:84%
And it's suggested,
it's pretty obvious

00:09:57.230 --> 00:10:00.650 align:middle line:84%
that early Americans believe
something extraordinary

00:10:00.650 --> 00:10:03.100 align:middle line:84%
about George Washington
that we have either

00:10:03.100 --> 00:10:06.350 align:middle line:90%
dismissed or forgotten.

00:10:06.350 --> 00:10:10.070 align:middle line:84%
They believed George
Washington was an awakened soul

00:10:10.070 --> 00:10:12.400 align:middle line:90%
and that he ascended.

00:10:12.400 --> 00:10:16.830 align:middle line:84%
Or at least they intended
for him to ascend.

00:10:16.830 --> 00:10:20.980 align:middle line:84%
So did he attain the rainbow
light body as I propose?

00:10:20.980 --> 00:10:25.420 align:middle line:84%
Is he now a resident of the
divine throne, like Enoch?

00:10:25.420 --> 00:10:29.770 align:middle line:84%
And if so, what does that mean
for the founding of America?

00:10:29.770 --> 00:10:32.280 align:middle line:84%
It seems as if, like
the original Jesus,

00:10:32.280 --> 00:10:36.270 align:middle line:84%
Washington has been white
washed by future generations,

00:10:36.270 --> 00:10:38.550 align:middle line:90%
and he's become lost.

00:10:38.550 --> 00:10:42.370 align:middle line:84%
But can you imagine if
imagery such as this

00:10:42.370 --> 00:10:47.070 align:middle line:84%
were attached to any
current era president?

00:10:47.070 --> 00:10:49.640 align:middle line:84%
Instead of a nation led
by conscious ascenders,

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:53.890 align:middle line:84%
we seem to have become a nation
led by unconscious descenders

00:10:53.890 --> 00:10:58.240 align:middle line:84%
who are apparently leading
us away from us spiritually

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:01.480 align:middle line:84%
or soul-based nation into a
nation devoid of anything that

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:04.570 align:middle line:90%
smacks of spirituality.

00:11:04.570 --> 00:11:08.960 align:middle line:84%
But America was founded upon the
separation of church and state.

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:12.290 align:middle line:84%
However, we are creating
a world of no religion

00:11:12.290 --> 00:11:15.260 align:middle line:84%
