00:22:57.030 --> 00:23:00.930 align:middle line:84%
It's found in the Hebrew
shamir, which rings of shimmer.

00:23:00.930 --> 00:23:03.310 align:middle line:84%
This was the name of the
miraculous stone cutter

00:23:03.310 --> 00:23:05.680 align:middle line:90%
used to build Solomon's Temple.

00:23:05.680 --> 00:23:09.360 align:middle line:84%
Sham is found in Baal
Shemit, a classification

00:23:09.360 --> 00:23:12.940 align:middle line:84%
of Jewish priests who
knew the name of the Lord.

00:23:12.940 --> 00:23:16.870 align:middle line:84%
Bit Shimti is the name of the
house where the wind or soul

00:23:16.870 --> 00:23:20.350 align:middle line:84%
was breathed into the first
human, Adapa, in the Sumerian

00:23:20.350 --> 00:23:21.285 align:middle line:90%
story.

00:23:21.285 --> 00:23:25.980 align:middle line:84%
Ni Shemit is the name of the
golden soul boat of Osiris.

00:23:25.980 --> 00:23:30.840 align:middle line:84%
Then finally, there's the word
shaman, or shaman, or soul

00:23:30.840 --> 00:23:32.690 align:middle line:90%
healer.

00:23:32.690 --> 00:23:36.490 align:middle line:84%
That's a lot of powerful words
revolving around the word sham

00:23:36.490 --> 00:23:42.170 align:middle line:84%
that are all congruent with the
ideals of peace and ascension.

00:23:42.170 --> 00:23:46.810 align:middle line:84%
Funny isn't it, that all these
words contain the word sham?

00:23:46.810 --> 00:23:50.330 align:middle line:84%
Shamatha is a practice
that anyone can do.

00:23:50.330 --> 00:23:53.790 align:middle line:84%
It really is a
science of the mind.

00:23:53.790 --> 00:23:58.070 align:middle line:84%
All you have to do is be mindful
and set your heart's power

00:23:58.070 --> 00:24:00.810 align:middle line:90%
of intention on peace.

00:24:00.810 --> 00:24:04.640 align:middle line:84%
And this links you with what
I call the heart's ascension

00:24:04.640 --> 00:24:06.462 align:middle line:90%
intelligence.

00:24:06.462 --> 00:24:09.630 align:middle line:84%
The Shamatha thankas
are meant, actually,

00:24:09.630 --> 00:24:17.260 align:middle line:84%
to be open eye meditations that
guide our mind into stillness.

00:24:17.260 --> 00:24:21.630 align:middle line:84%
Peacefully abiding means
we are at peace or feeling

00:24:21.630 --> 00:24:24.120 align:middle line:90%
whole and complete.

00:24:24.120 --> 00:24:26.700 align:middle line:84%
We know we are at
that ultimate peace

00:24:26.700 --> 00:24:30.730 align:middle line:84%
when the rainbow
bridge opens before us.

00:24:30.730 --> 00:24:32.800 align:middle line:84%
These illustrations
actually function

00:24:32.800 --> 00:24:34.970 align:middle line:84%
in a manner similar
to a cosmogram

00:24:34.970 --> 00:24:39.860 align:middle line:84%
or a mandala, a Sanskrit word
meaning circle and wholeness.

00:24:39.860 --> 00:24:45.210 align:middle line:84%
Mandalas are designed to help
us to go full circle as souls.

00:24:45.210 --> 00:24:48.550 align:middle line:10%
Mandalas are concentric
diagrams or holy patterns that

00:24:48.550 --> 00:24:52.300 align:middle line:10%
represent a universe or
cosmos metaphysically

00:24:52.300 --> 00:24:54.160 align:middle line:10%
and symbolically.

00:24:54.160 --> 00:24:56.760 align:middle line:84%
They are used as
meditation aids.

00:24:56.760 --> 00:24:58.500 align:middle line:84%
Hindus and Buddhists
use mandalas

00:24:58.500 --> 00:25:02.010 align:middle line:84%
to create imaginary
palaces or thrones

00:25:02.010 --> 00:25:06.160 align:middle line:84%
to focus the spiritual attention
of aspirants and adepts.

00:25:06.160 --> 00:25:10.350 align:middle line:90%
They are divine conduits.

00:25:10.350 --> 00:25:13.960 align:middle line:84%
The center point in the
circle is called the bindu.

00:25:13.960 --> 00:25:18.470 align:middle line:84%
The mandala binds the
aspirant to the divine.

00:25:18.470 --> 00:25:22.250 align:middle line:84%
And the bindu or bindu is
thought of as a seed, a sperm,

00:25:22.250 --> 00:25:25.260 align:middle line:84%
a drop, or a starting
point around which

00:25:25.260 --> 00:25:27.890 align:middle line:90%
the spiritual essence is drawn.

00:25:27.890 --> 00:25:31.820 align:middle line:10%
As the devotee draws in
the essence energies,

00:25:31.820 --> 00:25:35.520 align:middle line:10%
their own energies begin to
bind with the spiritual essence

00:25:35.520 --> 00:25:38.340 align:middle line:10%
and expand.

00:25:38.340 --> 00:25:42.250 align:middle line:84%
The word mandala is derived
from manda, or essence, and la,

00:25:42.250 --> 00:25:43.390 align:middle line:90%
or container.

00:25:43.390 --> 00:25:45.630 align:middle line:84%
Indeed, it is a container
of this essence,

00:25:45.630 --> 00:25:47.440 align:middle line:84%
and it is designed
to help our body

00:25:47.440 --> 00:25:51.880 align:middle line:84%
to become a container for
this essence, as well.

00:25:51.880 --> 00:25:53.630 align:middle line:84%
An additional purpose
of the mandala

00:25:53.630 --> 00:25:56.580 align:middle line:90%
is significant to our study.

00:25:56.580 --> 00:26:00.660 align:middle line:84%
That is because mandalas
symbolize the universe.

00:26:00.660 --> 00:26:03.560 align:middle line:84%
They are an active
form of meditation

00:26:03.560 --> 00:26:08.040 align:middle line:84%
that establish sacred
space, a pure Buddha

00:26:08.040 --> 00:26:11.620 align:middle line:84%
realm, and the abode of fully
realized beings or deities

00:26:11.620 --> 00:26:15.040 align:middle line:84%
where our ascended
higher self dwells.

00:26:15.040 --> 00:26:17.870 align:middle line:84%
Just having a mandala
in our presence

00:26:17.870 --> 00:26:22.120 align:middle line:90%
establishes sacred space.

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:25.740 align:middle line:84%
The sacred space of the mandala
is actually viewed as separate

00:26:25.740 --> 00:26:30.040 align:middle line:84%
from ordinary or profane
reality, the normal world.

00:26:30.040 --> 00:26:33.090 align:middle line:84%
And by visualizing pure
lands or Buddha realms,

00:26:33.090 --> 00:26:35.880 align:middle line:84%
one learns to
dwell in that place

00:26:35.880 --> 00:26:39.090 align:middle line:84%
and experience oneself
as a pure being.

00:26:39.090 --> 00:26:42.850 align:middle line:90%


00:26:42.850 --> 00:26:46.690 align:middle line:84%
Buddhists teach that meditating
on the symbols of the mandala

00:26:46.690 --> 00:26:49.250 align:middle line:84%
opens one to progressively
deeper levels

00:26:49.250 --> 00:26:52.650 align:middle line:84%
of the unconscious until
the meditator experiences

00:26:52.650 --> 00:26:56.150 align:middle line:84%
a mystical sense of oneness
with the divine realm.

00:26:56.150 --> 00:26:58.310 align:middle line:84%
The mandala represents
all the levels

00:26:58.310 --> 00:27:01.140 align:middle line:84%
of energy of the perfect
spiritual body working

00:27:01.140 --> 00:27:05.910 align:middle line:84%
in balance by allowing our mind
to recognize that wholeness

00:27:05.910 --> 00:27:09.050 align:middle line:84%
and perfection is
our original state,

00:27:09.050 --> 00:27:12.430 align:middle line:84%
and this is a state
of pure peace.

00:27:12.430 --> 00:27:15.890 align:middle line:84%
Here's another example of a
golden Dorje from the Rubin

00:27:15.890 --> 00:27:16.960 align:middle line:90%
Museum.

00:27:16.960 --> 00:27:21.850 align:middle line:84%
It looks like an exploding
star or a wormhole to me.

00:27:21.850 --> 00:27:25.280 align:middle line:84%
The path of calm abiding images
that we've been exploring

00:27:25.280 --> 00:27:27.606 align:middle line:90%
had much more to show me.

00:27:27.606 --> 00:27:28.980 align:middle line:84%
Soon after learning
about them, I

00:27:28.980 --> 00:27:32.430 align:middle line:84%
became transfixed by a
series of unusual 15th

00:27:32.430 --> 00:27:34.710 align:middle line:84%
to 17th century
Russian Last Judgment

00:27:34.710 --> 00:27:38.690 align:middle line:84%
icons, which depict a
serpent ladder linking

00:27:38.690 --> 00:27:43.660 align:middle line:84%
Earth with Jesus's
cosmic throne, or Sion.

00:27:43.660 --> 00:27:46.750 align:middle line:84%
The icon shown here features
the extraordinary symbolism

00:27:46.750 --> 00:27:50.650 align:middle line:84%
of this style of Last
Judgment iconography.

00:27:50.650 --> 00:27:53.980 align:middle line:84%
What we see are five
horizontal zones

00:27:53.980 --> 00:27:57.270 align:middle line:84%
with a central access,
a tree or a pillar,

00:27:57.270 --> 00:28:03.740 align:middle line:84%
around which climbs a serpentine
rope, chain, or rosary of orbs.

00:28:03.740 --> 00:28:09.540 align:middle line:84%
Each zone represents a level
of light, or perhaps vibration.

00:28:09.540 --> 00:28:12.745 align:middle line:84%
As Dr. David Goldfrank notes
in his article, A Problem

00:28:12.745 --> 00:28:16.550 align:middle line:84%
of Last Judgment Iconography,
the snake suddenly

00:28:16.550 --> 00:28:19.910 align:middle line:84%
appeared without warning
in late medieval Ukrainian

00:28:19.910 --> 00:28:22.230 align:middle line:84%
and Russian Last
Judgment iconography.

00:28:22.230 --> 00:28:25.000 align:middle line:84%
But nobody knows
where it came from.

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:28.250 align:middle line:84%
It usually has 20 or
more rings representing

00:28:28.250 --> 00:28:33.020 align:middle line:84%
what Goldfrank calls stellar
toll booths through which

00:28:33.020 --> 00:28:36.810 align:middle line:90%
the soul must pass after death.

00:28:36.810 --> 00:28:40.950 align:middle line:10%
The resurrected Jesus sits on
an arching bow in a blue sphere

00:28:40.950 --> 00:28:43.100 align:middle line:10%
in the higher zones.

00:28:43.100 --> 00:28:45.030 align:middle line:90%
Stellar toll booth.

00:28:45.030 --> 00:28:48.250 align:middle line:84%
I love it when academics
speak like this.

00:28:48.250 --> 00:28:50.770 align:middle line:84%
And personally, I think
they'd find great illumination

00:28:50.770 --> 00:28:53.100 align:middle line:84%
if instead of using
the word toll booth,

00:28:53.100 --> 00:28:55.530 align:middle line:84%
they use the word
star gate instead,

00:28:55.530 --> 00:28:59.910 align:middle line:84%
because this is obviously
what's being described here.

00:28:59.910 --> 00:29:04.000 align:middle line:84%
And further, the serpent
symbolizes the cosmic conduit,

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:08.390 align:middle line:84%
just like in the Tibetan images
of the Path of Calm Abiding.

00:29:08.390 --> 00:29:10.470 align:middle line:10%
Is this the source
of this imagery?

00:29:10.470 --> 00:29:13.770 align:middle line:84%
Or does it come
from somewhere else?

00:29:13.770 --> 00:29:16.440 align:middle line:84%
Goldfrank tells us that
the rings on the serpent

00:29:16.440 --> 00:29:20.020 align:middle line:84%
represent the torments the
human soul must go through

00:29:20.020 --> 00:29:23.790 align:middle line:84%
in order to return to
the kingdom of heaven.

00:29:23.790 --> 00:29:27.960 align:middle line:84%
In my view, this serpent rope
is a sort of umbilical cord

00:29:27.960 --> 00:29:30.530 align:middle line:84%
that can be thought of
as the spiritual ladder,

00:29:30.530 --> 00:29:32.410 align:middle line:90%
or stairway to heaven.

00:29:32.410 --> 00:29:36.330 align:middle line:84%
It literally is the
star gate to God.

00:29:36.330 --> 00:29:41.620 align:middle line:84%
It represents the soul's
path to ascension.

00:29:41.620 --> 00:29:45.090 align:middle line:84%
In Secret of Sion, I propose
that these cosmic toll booths

00:29:45.090 --> 00:29:47.600 align:middle line:84%
are, in fact, star gates
that the soul passes through

00:29:47.600 --> 00:29:49.150 align:middle line:90%
on its way to Sion.

00:29:49.150 --> 00:29:50.980 align:middle line:90%
They're soul gates.

00:29:50.980 --> 00:29:55.260 align:middle line:84%
And these images map
the soul's journey home.

00:29:55.260 --> 00:29:57.540 align:middle line:84%
Let's take a look
at another example.

00:29:57.540 --> 00:30:01.120 align:middle line:84%
In the lowest zone here
on the left hand side,

00:30:01.120 --> 00:30:03.810 align:middle line:84%
we see the righteous
souls in line

00:30:03.810 --> 00:30:07.830 align:middle line:84%
waiting to enter past St. Peter,
who stands at the golden door

00:30:07.830 --> 00:30:10.020 align:middle line:84%
or tower with
golden gates guarded

00:30:10.020 --> 00:30:13.360 align:middle line:84%
by a seraph, a celestial
being that dwells normally

00:30:13.360 --> 00:30:15.810 align:middle line:84%
at the throne of God but
has apparently come here

00:30:15.810 --> 00:30:18.360 align:middle line:90%
to retrieve these souls.

00:30:18.360 --> 00:30:20.750 align:middle line:84%
Once again, we see
the ascended Christ

00:30:20.750 --> 00:30:24.710 align:middle line:84%
is shown enthroned and radiant
at the end of the serpent's

00:30:24.710 --> 00:30:28.240 align:middle line:84%
mouth, or at the
end of the wormhole.

00:30:28.240 --> 00:30:32.350 align:middle line:84%
He is in heaven, enthroned
upon a sapphire blue orb,

00:30:32.350 --> 00:30:35.020 align:middle line:84%
ringed with stars and
flanked by Mary and John

00:30:35.020 --> 00:30:37.520 align:middle line:84%
the Baptist, the two
people who helped him most

00:30:37.520 --> 00:30:39.990 align:middle line:90%
during his earthly ascension.

00:30:39.990 --> 00:30:43.360 align:middle line:84%
He's also surrounded by
mysterious celestial or star

00:30:43.360 --> 00:30:47.550 align:middle line:84%
beings, who are referred to in
Hebrews as the just humans made

00:30:47.550 --> 00:30:49.460 align:middle line:90%
perfect.

00:30:49.460 --> 00:30:51.570 align:middle line:84%
As we notice here,
beneath Jesus is

00:30:51.570 --> 00:30:55.260 align:middle line:84%
a cross mounted to
a box or an alter

00:30:55.260 --> 00:30:58.480 align:middle line:84%
and attended by two angels,
and other instruments

00:30:58.480 --> 00:31:00.910 align:middle line:84%
of the passion, including
the Spear of Destiny

00:31:00.910 --> 00:31:03.680 align:middle line:90%
and the rod with a sponge.

00:31:03.680 --> 00:31:06.300 align:middle line:84%
In Russia, this
assembly of symbols

00:31:06.300 --> 00:31:11.010 align:middle line:84%
was called Etimasia, or the
throne of the Second Coming,

00:31:11.010 --> 00:31:13.490 align:middle line:84%
and will be retrieved
and reassembled

00:31:13.490 --> 00:31:17.370 align:middle line:84%
by the returning Christ at
the time of the Second Coming.

00:31:17.370 --> 00:31:22.220 align:middle line:84%
The Greek verb hetoimase means
to prepare, or preparation,

00:31:22.220 --> 00:31:24.670 align:middle line:90%
as in the Second Coming.

00:31:24.670 --> 00:31:28.340 align:middle line:84%
It's ever present in these
Russian Last Judgment images

00:31:28.340 --> 00:31:31.590 align:middle line:84%
because it will be
deployed at judgment day

00:31:31.590 --> 00:31:34.770 align:middle line:84%
when the Christ or
messiah returns.

00:31:34.770 --> 00:31:36.320 align:middle line:84%
In my book "The
Judgment Day Device,"

00:31:36.320 --> 00:31:40.160 align:middle line:84%
I propose that this throne is
in fact the fully assembled

00:31:40.160 --> 00:31:44.580 align:middle line:84%
Ark of the Covenant, the throne
chariot or soul transportation

00:31:44.580 --> 00:31:45.560 align:middle line:90%
device.

00:31:45.560 --> 00:31:48.900 align:middle line:84%
When the rod of Aaron, seen
here in the Ark of the Covenant,

00:31:48.900 --> 00:31:52.600 align:middle line:84%
is attached to the
golden box of the Ark

00:31:52.600 --> 00:31:55.070 align:middle line:84%
and the two tablets
are placed on top

00:31:55.070 --> 00:32:01.240 align:middle line:84%
of that rod of enlightenment,
it forms the throne of Christ.

00:32:01.240 --> 00:32:04.810 align:middle line:84%
So in my view, the
Tibetan imagery

00:32:04.810 --> 00:32:09.340 align:middle line:84%
is very likely the candidate
for the source of this imagery.

00:32:09.340 --> 00:32:11.790 align:middle line:84%
And once again, we
are looking at images

00:32:11.790 --> 00:32:15.460 align:middle line:84%
that are designed to assist
the soul in mapping it's

00:32:15.460 --> 00:32:18.980 align:middle line:90%
ascension to the divine realms.

00:32:18.980 --> 00:32:22.350 align:middle line:10%
More fantastically, I can
envision the original source

00:32:22.350 --> 00:32:25.910 align:middle line:10%
of this imagery as coming
from a divine place

00:32:25.910 --> 00:32:30.420 align:middle line:10%
elsewhere, deep in the cosmos.

00:32:30.420 --> 00:32:32.190 align:middle line:84%
All of these images
we've looked at,

00:32:32.190 --> 00:32:35.040 align:middle line:84%
from George Washington on
the rainbow in the US Capitol

00:32:35.040 --> 00:32:37.850 align:middle line:84%
to the Tibetan Path
of Calm Abiding

00:32:37.850 --> 00:32:40.020 align:middle line:84%
to the Russian Last
Judgment images

00:32:40.020 --> 00:32:43.880 align:middle line:84%
help us to recognize
that our soul ascends

00:32:43.880 --> 00:32:49.650 align:middle line:84%
via a divine or cosmic conduit
that we today call a wormhole.

00:32:49.650 --> 00:32:52.600 align:middle line:84%
These conduits remind me
a bit of the beanstalk

00:32:52.600 --> 00:32:55.030 align:middle line:84%
Jack ascended to in
the land of the giant

00:32:55.030 --> 00:32:58.400 align:middle line:84%
after he planted the magic
seeds in the fairytale.

00:32:58.400 --> 00:33:00.180 align:middle line:84%
And in the next
episode, we're going

00:33:00.180 --> 00:33:03.880 align:middle line:84%
to explore our souls
as sacred star seeds

00:33:03.880 --> 00:33:05.890 align:middle line:84%
and see how this
idea could truly

00:33:05.890 --> 00:33:11.120 align:middle line:84%
transform our world into a
truly green civilization.

00:33:11.120 --> 00:33:14.660 align:middle line:84%
Until next time, be humble,
let your light shine.

00:33:14.660 --> 00:33:16.360 align:middle line:90%
Namaste.

